---
---

<header class="hud">
  <div class="hud__score">Skor<span id="score">0</span></div>
  <div class="hud__score">Tur<span id="round">0/10</span></div>
  <div class="hud__score">Sekme<span id="bounces">—</span></div>
  <div class="hud__score">Rekor<span id="best">0</span></div>
  <button id="restart" class="hud__btn" type="button">Yeniden başla</button>
</header>

<div class="board-wrap">
  <canvas id="board" width="540" height="420" aria-label="Sek Tahmin alanı"></canvas>
  <div id="overlay" class="overlay" role="status" aria-live="polite">
    <div class="overlay__inner">
      <h2 id="overlay-title">Sek Tahmin</h2>
      <p id="overlay-body">Yeşil noktadan giren topun, oka göre <strong>K sekme</strong> sonra perimetreden çıkacağı noktayı kenara tıklayarak işaretle. Enter/Boşluk: başla.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<p class="vec" aria-live="polite">
  <span class="vec__pill">Yön: <span id="dir">—</span></span>
  <span class="vec__pill">Giriş: <span id="entry">—</span></span>
</p>
